node.text: You haven’t lost that touch! And I only just saw the muffins in the Ferris wheel. So cute. 💕👌

Blessed Mother’s Day! Chiffon Cake baked for yesterday’s filming at Mediacorp. Happy to be invited by Channel 8 to share about baking on their ongoing variety show《健康那些事- Get Fit With Me》. This meaningful program is specially tailored during COVID-19 to educate and entertain audience especially elderly when everyone has to stay home.
.
.
You can catch me on TV with hosts Dasmond Koh, Kym Ng and Felicia Chin on 21 May 2020, Thursday , 10am-10.30am. (Food segment) Stay tuned! .
.
.
Swipe 🔙☝️ for more bakes which I’ve baked using Blue Jacket flour and brought along for the filming. Glad the pastries are well received!.
.
.

Due to the circuit breaker & social distancing measures, I’m unable to share photos of the filming. Do not worry, everyone on set wears a mask and only takes it off during filming. We also comply with the social distancing rule and stand apart from one another. .
.
.
.
.
.

@nomninjas Thanks Iris! All natural flavor and colourings  using premium ingredients like Vanilla Bean , Uji Matcha & Valrhona Cocoa. 😊
Happy Mother’s Day!!!! This looks super good 💕
Wow looks so yummy. Looking forward to catch the show! 👍🏻👍🏻

@ivyhpyv Hi, recipe is adapted from my blog’s "Matcha Chiffon Cake". Goggle for it, then adapt by dividing the yolk batter and meringue into 3 equal portions and flavored one portion with vanilla bean paste, one portion with Uji matcha powder and one portion with Valrhona cocoa powder will do.
@msjaniceeats 谢谢，也祝你一样母亲节快乐，天天快乐！❤️❤️❤️
Date Engraved on my wall! Definitely will stay tune for your appearance on TV 😍😍
Wa niceeee!! Looking forward to watching your episode! 😉
Wow!!!for sure will stay tune💕💕💕 tall & beautiful chiffon cake as usual 👍👍❤️
@mondaymunchings Thank you for your kind words 😊
this is absolutely stunning! you're amazing 😍🙌
I want to eat this marble cake. 😍
@naturalvitaminsea Thank you, it’s baked specially for a filming and the variety show was broadcasted on TV yesterday. You can hop over to my latest post or IGTV to take a look. 😊
@whattoeat2018 Thanks been a long time since I baked chiffon cake and this one is baked specially for my filming and sharing for Channel 8 show on TV. 😄
Love chiffon cake- always so light, airy & never too sweet. Almost guilt -free! 😅
You haven’t lost that touch! And I only just saw the muffins in the Ferris wheel. So cute. 💕👌
